01:00:52.853 --> 01:00:54.655
I just-- I just love
going to the movies.

1219
01:00:54.688 --> 01:00:56.757
Yeah. man.
that's how it starts.

1220
01:00:58.627 --> 01:01:00.794
Most people come to movies
to escape their lives.

1221
01:01:00.828 --> 01:01:02.930
but people like us.

1222
01:01:02.963 --> 01:01:06.635
we come here because
movies make life make sense.

1223
01:01:07.868 --> 01:01:10.838
Out here. man.
world's full of lies.

1224
01:01:11.705 --> 01:01:15.442
But in there. they tell
the lie that tells the truth.

1225
01:01:15.476 --> 01:01:18.045
And the truth about you and me
is we're filmmakers.

1226
01:01:20.114 --> 01:01:21.916
We just haven't made
our films.

1227
01:01:23.450 --> 01:01:24.485
Yet.

1228
01:01:34.728 --> 01:01:35.729
"Yet."

1229
01:01:55.249 --> 01:01:56.383
Whoa.

1230
01:02:03.924 --> 01:02:05.359
