1406
01:11:51.478 --> 01:11:53.080
And she said it was beautiful.

1407
01:11:56.017 --> 01:12:00.121
So. yeah. you're totally
gonna be a writer someday.

1408
01:12:02.290 --> 01:12:03.191
Man.

1409
