1463
01:15:14.448 --> 01:15:15.983
Important thoughts like this.

1464
01:15:17.318 --> 01:15:19.253
<i>Beatbox Bri. take one!</i>

1465
01:15:19.286 --> 01:15:21.122
Um... Shit. uh...

